# Review Gate

After implementing a ticket, do not treat self-check in the same session as final review.

1. Mark the ticket `in_review`.
2. Request a separate review using `process/ai-factory/REVIEW_PASS.md` (second agent, Bugbot, or human).
3. Mark `done` only after PASS + green CI.

When acting as the review agent: report PASS/FAIL and findings; do not implement fixes unless asked.
